Short map, 26~ seconds. I made this to go along with a tutorial i will be posting shortly about filters. 

This is my last short map for a long time i reckon. I have a few big map projects that i am working on from here on that will be fairly lengthy and hopefully fun. Expect my next release to be something along the lines of sina. (not counting the csgo version of this which will be released with the tutorial)



Have fun!
